  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">十年前的一篇AMC文章</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\">很多家長詢問我關於AMC的一些資訊（它已正式列入學習履歷認證，參與的人數勢必逐步攀升）。<br />\n我收錄過宗翰老師十年前一篇關於AMC的分析文章，經老師同意，在此和大家分享，希望讓大家對AMC有更深入的了解。<br />\n（日後我會繼續邀文，請老師提供專業看法）</span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/715356886083666/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/715356886083666/</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284739413-e84773ea.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284771433-46a23d79.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284728446-0a38464e.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284745607-53949ffe.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284760849-f989c8a8.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284714324-9d314e32.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
